{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7accae5873","title":"对随军南下干部的讲话（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5c76741e3c","index":0,"year":1944,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"7accae5873"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui2","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1943-1949卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui2a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"01061320aa","type":"title","text":"对随军南下干部的讲话（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"7accae5873"},{"id":"ab903ec960","type":"paragraph","text":"还要学会两种本领，头一个是松树的本领，第二个是柳树的本领。松树发育成长，不怕刮风下雪，严寒之下也能巍然屹立。松树有“原则性”；柳树插到哪里都能活，一到春天，枝长叶茂，随风飘荡，十分可爱。柳树有“灵活性”。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"7accae5873"},{"id":"b48aa41525","type":"paragraph","text":"一个共产党员应该有松树的“原则性”和柳树的“灵活性”，缺一不行。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"7accae5873"}],"page":{"id":"f517a8ce92","publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"7accae5873","start":46,"end":46}}}},"__N_SSG":true}